---
import { menuEnglish } from "./SideBar.astro";
export const linksTo = "text-primary underline hover:decoration-2 underline-offset-2";
---

<section class="mb-8 break-words hyphens-auto">
  <p class="mb-4">
    I develop creative systems that merge mathematics, computation, and music through structural
    analogies.
  </p>
  <p class="mb-4">
    All for real-time algorithmic composition, my current projects include
    <a href="https://rubygems.org/gems/modular_forms" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class={linksTo}
      >modular forms</a
    > (SageMath/LMFDB-inspired) and
    <a id="projects" href={menuEnglish.projectsMenu.href} rel="noopener" class={`${linksTo} `}>
      multidimensional figurate number generators</a
    >
    with over <strong>26,000 downloads</strong>, as well as
    <a
      href="https://topos.live/#ziffers_tonnetz"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener"
      class={`${linksTo}`}>ts-tonnetz</a
    >.
  </p>
  <p>
    I have published a
    <a
      href="https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-031-07015-0_30"
      target="_blank"
      class={`${linksTo}`}
      rel="noopener"
    >
      Scopus-indexed article</a
    >
    in Mathematical Music Theory, serve as a peer reviewer for The European Physical Journal, contribute
    to international open-source projects, and teach postgraduate courses.
  </p>
</section>
